{"sections":{"main":{"type":"page__main","disabled":true,"settings":{"spacing_top":100,"spacing_bottom":100,"color_scheme":"color__bg-body","color_background":"#ffffff","color_text":"","color_border":"color__border-divider-1","enable_color_fade":false,"style_border":"","layout_x_alignment":"justify-start","enable_margin":true,"enable_max_width":true,"visibility":""}},"text_ReNbFi":{"type":"text","name":"t:sections.text.name","settings":{"heading":"DRM + GAMEPLAN","content":"<p>The partnership to champion mental health. DRM and GamePlan work together to navigate the pressures of school, career, and life. <\/p><p>Through education, discussion, and support our teams believe we can make measurable differences in the lives of millions. Join us as we grow the conversation, build positive mental attitudes and create a world where no one struggles alone. <\/p>","button_label":"","button_url":"","spacing_top":100,"spacing_bottom":100,"color_scheme":"color__bg-body","color_background":"#ffffff","color_text":"","color_border":"color__border-divider-1","color_button":"btn btn--secondary","enable_color_fade":false,"style_border":"","style_text_alignment":"text-center","layout_x_alignment":"justify-center","layout_column_width":80,"enable_margin":true,"visibility":""}},"content_grid_nhRx6H":{"type":"content-grid","blocks":{"content_yU3YBw":{"type":"content","settings":{"heading":"","content":"<p>There would be no GamePlan without Drew R. Miller. He was an original supporter, and pushed our team with an unwavering belief. A friend, and catalyst that sparked the action required to turn a dream into reality. <\/p><p>Now, we partner with the foundation created in his honor to provide support and resources for young and upcoming professionals everywhere. <\/p><p>More than a partnership, this is a shared mission to build a stronger future. One in which no one suffers in silence, and the tools, people, and education are always available for those navigating the pressures of life. <\/p><p>GamePlan proudly donates a percentage of profits to the DRM Foundation. <\/p>","button_label":"","url":"","show_image_as_background":false,"enable_autoplay":true,"enable_mute_toggle":true,"enable_loop":true,"spacing_minimum_height":250,"enable_padding":true,"color_scheme":"color__bg-body color__text","color_border":"","color_text":"color__text","color_button":"btn--small btn--outline","enable_gradient":false,"text_position":"below","layout_y_alignment":"justify-end","layout_x_alignment":"left","layout_row_span":"row-span-1","layout_col_span":"col-span-1 md:col-span-1"}},"content_Kbxk6r":{"type":"content","settings":{"heading":"","content":"","button_label":"","url":"","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/DRM-test.png","show_image_as_background":true,"enable_autoplay":true,"enable_mute_toggle":true,"enable_loop":true,"spacing_minimum_height":500,"enable_padding":true,"color_scheme":"color__bg-body color__text","color_border":"","color_text":"color__text","color_button":"btn--small btn--outline","enable_gradient":false,"text_position":"below","layout_y_alignment":"justify-end","layout_x_alignment":"left","layout_row_span":"row-span-1","layout_col_span":"col-span-1 md:col-span-1"}}},"block_order":["content_yU3YBw","content_Kbxk6r"],"name":"t:sections.content_grid.name","settings":{"heading":"","content":"","button_label":"","button_url":"","spacing_top":0,"spacing_bottom":0,"color_scheme":"color__bg-body","color_background":"#ffffff","color_text":"","color_border":"color__border-divider-1","color_button":"btn btn--secondary","enable_color_fade":false,"style_border":"","layout_row_desktop":2,"layout_row_mobile":1,"layout_x_alignment":"justify-between","enable_margin":true,"enable_split":false,"enable_split_heading":false,"visibility":""}}},"order":["main","text_ReNbFi","content_grid_nhRx6H"]}